
Welcome to ld-hotcorners!

Try all of the corners out. Simply drag your mouse to a corner.

Top-left       =  File Manager
Top-right      =  Toggles Picom
Lower-right    =  Exit Menu
Lower-left     =  Terminal

Once you get used to the bounceback, quite a handy little script.

There is a menu entry for ld-hotcorners under 'Configuration'
in order to change settings.


To use ld-hotcorners on login, go to ~/.config/openbox/autostart, 
and under autostart add:  ld-hotcorners --daemon &
